<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45292,45524,45792,46020</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Albert</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45368,45640,45880,46096</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rondoline&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Rondoline&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぅ……、ズルイ、ズルイだ、&lt;Rody&gt;たん……。
おらを置いてけぼりにして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How horrible...How cruel of this world, Miss &lt;Rody&gt;! I was left behind!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、私？　何かしたっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? What do you mean?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おらよりも先に、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に呼び捨てにされただ！
これをズルイと言わずして、なんと言うだーよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You've levelled up your relationship with &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; faster than me! She is now calling you without honorifics! That's cruelty, I'm telling you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれ？　そうだっけ？
そんだけ、距離感が縮まったってことかな～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh just that little thingy? We just became a little closer that's all~?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おらも、もっと&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;と距離を縮めてーだ！
早く呼び捨てにされたり、あだ名で呼んでほしいだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to be the closerest with &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! I want her to drop the "Mister"! I want her to come up with a nickname!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あだ名？　例えばどんなのがいいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A nickname? For example?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46024</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そら、『アルちゃん』とか『アルベっち』とか？
あとは、『アルルン』なんてのもいいなー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's see, how about "Al" or "Alby"~? Oh, oh "Aberber" is good too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_106_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ざんね～ん、一生無理！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Too bad~! You won't get there in a lifetime, buddy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
